::Kluster::

Kluster's eyes widen at the news. "Maximal Elders DEAD?!"

He blinks a few times, absorbing the shock. "Hmm. The Cybertronian Fire 
doesn't have functional engines. As far as I can tell, the only ships that do 
are the Alliance base and the Iron Fist, and they are both hostile. We can't 
get to Cybertron."
